metadata.name: Beginning
metadata.description: Adrift in life, this girl felt disgusted. She spun on the spot in the unknown. The cold thought of "who am I?" stirred her imagination. A frightened naked body stared at her from the reflection. She stepped closer and touched her wet face. Her hand slid over her cold skin, and the desire to explore herself released her hand lower. And the feeling of love began to fill her empty soul. And her soul began to demand freedom. A blue wave began to hit the scans of her body's bare mountains. The weightless and almost transparent sea listened to the curves. The airlifted the water and touched her body, pushing her to find herself
